phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common accessibility mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| No content description | Add description |
| No label | Add label |
| No role | Add role |
| No heading | Add heading |
| Wrong description | Use null for decorative |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Content description
IconButton(
    onClick = {},
    modifier = Modifier.semantics {
        contentDescription = "Delete item"
    }
) { Icon(Icons.Default.Delete, null) }

// 2. Label
TextField(
    value = "",
    onValueChange = {},
    label = { Text("Enter text") }
)

// 3. Role
Box(
    modifier = Modifier
        .clickable {}
        .semantics { role = Role.Button }
)

// 4. Heading
Text(
    "Section Title",
    modifier = Modifier.semantics { heading() }
)

// 5. Decorative
Image(
    painter = painterResource(R.drawable.decorative),
    contentDescription = null // Decorative
)
```
